ke-up Reel Unit.'),(77,1,'SC-F6330','1620','Pressure Motor PRS Initialization Error','1. Ink Holder<br>2. Main Board','Initialization was not completed within the specified duration.','1. Check the following connections for abnormalities such as connector disconnection or a broken cable, and ensure cables are connected correctly.<br>- Ink Holder (Decompression Pump) to Main Board<br>- Sub-B Board to Main Board<br>2. Replace the Ink Holder.<br>3. If the problem persists, replace the Main Board.'),(78,1,'SC-F6330','1621','Pressure Motor Pressure/Suction Switching Error','1. Ink Holder<br>2. Main Board','Pressure/suction was not completed within the specified duration.','1. Check the following connections for abnormalities such as connector disconnection or a broken cable, and ensure cables are connected correctly.<br>- Ink Holder (Decompression Pump) to Main Board<br>- Sub-B Board to Main Board<br>2. Replace the Ink Holder.<br>3. If the problem persists, replace the Main Board.'),(79,1,'SC-F6330','1622','Pressure Motor Driving Time-Out Error','1. Ink Holder<br>2. Main Board','The switching operation was not completed within the specified duration.','1. Check the following connections for abnormalities such as connector disconnection or a broken cable, and ensure cables are connected correctly.<br>- Ink Holder (Decompression Pump) to Main Board<br>- Sub-B Board to Main Board<br>2. Replace the Ink Holder.<br>3. If the problem persists, replace the Main Board.'),(80,1,'SC-F6330','1623','Pressure Motor Continuous Rotation Error','1. Ink Holder<br>2. Main Board','the control terminal (Vre terminal) of the Motor Driver was shortcircuited.','1. Check the following connections for abnormalities such as connector disconnection or a broken cable, and ensure cables are connected correctly.<br>- Ink Holder (Decompression Pump) to Main Board<br>- Sub-B Board to Main Board<br>2. Replace the Ink Holder.<br>3. If the problem persists, replace the Main Board.'),(81,1,'SC-F6330','1A23'